item.title: RUGBY: SOAS fail to knock out IC
item.author: Edric Ramirez-Valdez,
item.description: On Wednesday the 11th November, IC 2nd XV travelled to Regents’ Park to face the School of Oriental and Asian Studies in the first cup game of the season. After four consecutive wins for IC, the last two of which were by over 50 points, playing a team from a different league meant a solid …
